data.name: labelAbout.Text
data.value:
GeoTransformer is developed by Kārlis Gaņģis with a single purpose in mind - to implement a set of features that help everyday routine for geocachers - updating the geocache information on their GPS devices from newest pocket queries.
GeoTransformer is distributed free of charge. However, if you want to express your gratitude for the application you can donate using the PayPal link above (will open in browser).
To communicate with the author to report bugs or request features or just to express opinions visit the GeoTransformer home page using the link in the toolbar.
